event.title: FSFE booth at NLLGG Software Freedom Day 2018 in Utrecht, The Netherlands

body.p: The Dutch Linux user group (NLLGG) is celebrating Software Freedom Day 2018 with a series of talks and the FSFE will be there with a booth. Location: Kranenburg Praktijkonderwijs, Tamboersdijk 9, 3582 TZ, Utrecht, The Netherlands. Time: 10.00-16.00.
